# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Branch  | Supported             |
| ------- | --------------------- |
| main    | :white_check_mark:    |
| dev     | :x:                   |
| testing | :construction_worker: |

### Reporting a Vulnerability

Please open an issue: [Bug Report](https://github.com/grm34/mobinfo/issues/new/choose)
